.SH NAME
.PP
traceOff \- Turn off the database engine program tracking and export tracking
results to binary files.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\f[B]\f[I]db.traceOff( <dumpFile>, [isDumpLocal] )\f[]\f[]
.SH CATEGORY
.PP
Sdb
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Turn off the database engine program tracking and export tracking results to
binary files.
.SH PARAMETERS
.PP
.TS
